Deborah Walley https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deborah_Walley 0 Deborah Walley (August 12, 1941 – May 10, 2001) was an American actress noted for playing the title role in Gidget Goes Hawaiian (1961) and in several Beach Party films.
